casebody.data:
HAYWARD
v.
S.C. (OSUCH) S237174 Supreme Court of California March 1, 2017

Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

Dismissed and remanded to CA 1/2. The "Joint Request for Order Dismissing Review Given Entry of Judgment Following Settlement," filed by the parties on January 27, 2017, is granted. The "Request for Order Directing Nonpublication of Court of Appeal Opinion Upon Dismissal of Review," filed January 27, 2017, and the "Request to Depublish," filed February 14, 2017, are both denied.
